        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5403294c-5390-46ba-a246-4bb6108253c0).Image",
        "Description": "FROM: Diana Burnwood\rTO: Tobias Rieper\r\r47, the situation is dire. The FRANCHISE in close behind. I suggest we make a detour. This ought to make them stand down.\r\rThere is a manor nearby. Now, my intel shows that a famous PI, Phinas Whitmer, an American lawyer, Ford Jr., as well as Betty W., a FRANCHISE informant, is here to investigate your case files. Stage accidents for the first two, 47. We cannot afford an investigation into non-FRANCHISE, non-target kills.\r\rUse the boat, 47. Quickly!",
